### Create a new Hackathon Event
POST http://localhost:5002/api/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "HackSphere Global 2026",
    "description": "An advanced polyglot microservices hackathon for tech enthusiasts.",
    "startDate": "2026-07-20T09:00:00.000Z",
    "endDate": "2026-07-21T09:00:00.000Z",
    "maxTeamSize": 4,
    "creatorId": "64a2b1234567890abcdef123"
}

###

### Get All Events
GET http://localhost:5002/api/events